### [Judges Chapter 18](../../../bib/kjv/jdg018.htm#001.md)

[Judges](../../../bib/kjv/jdg001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">jdg 18:0</span></span>

Overview

[Jdg 18:1](../../../bib/kjv/jdg018.htm#001.md), The Danites send five men
to seek out an inheritance; [Jdg 18:3](../../../bib/kjv/jdg018.htm#003.md),
At the house of Micah they consult with Jonathan, and are encouraged on
their way; [Jdg 18:7](../../../bib/kjv/jdg018.htm#007.md), They search
Laish, and bring back news of good hope; [Jdg
18:11](../../../bib/kjv/jdg018.htm#011.md), Six hundred men are sent to
surprise it; [Jdg 18:14](../../../bib/kjv/jdg018.htm#014.md), In their way
they rob Micah of his priest and his consecrated things; [Jdg
18:27](../../../bib/kjv/jdg018.htm#027.md), They win Laish, and call it
Dan; [Jdg 18:30](../../../bib/kjv/jdg018.htm#030.md), They set up idolatry,
wherein Jonathan inherits the priesthood.

